      <div class="msgContentFrame">Pretty good so far, great way to make money (like every other craft besides maybe cooking at this point) early on and it only gets better the higher your skill goes.  I was sitting on nearly half a million gil earned from GS before I decided to stop crafting and do some fighting.  The description on the official FFXIV sums it up about right: high risk, high reward.  You can easily lose 10-20k on a single synth but if you are successful you can make 4 times what it cost to make.</div>
