      <div class="msgContentFrame">I like it so far, quite easy to lvl for profit at the moment if you think it out right. <br />May change in the future off course. <br />I was planning to be a smith, but Im currently 10 smith 13 goldsmith, it is that easy. <br />Sitting on only ~300k myself, but my pug is lvl 16 too ;) <br />Like in FF11, goldsmith goes really well with mining. After that it depends on the synth. <br /> <br />What is good for now in goldsmith is that a lot of receipt can be made into end product w/o using other craft materials (like rings, gorget) makes it easier than for other craft. <br />That is also a kind of downfall as goldsmith seems really crowded on all serveurs at the moment and money may be harder to get sooner than with other crafts. <br /> <br />for me, I will carry on leveling both, making money on GS while there is money to be made. Once it gets harder I plan to switch to Smith mainly. <br /></div>
